0.3 series
- Initial usable version. 
- Major features: character sheets, power cards, custom dice rolling and a glossary.

0.4 series
- Support for Foundry 0.7.x.
- Improved tooltips which display HTML and don't underlap the sidebar.
- Sheet UI tweaks, with all elements saving correctly and better use of vertical space.
- Power cards now fit into smaller areas such as the default chatlog. Power messages in the chat log can be popped out into their own window.
- Status effect editing (just access to the builtin cosmetic features).
- Power macros, mostly useful for targeting. See MacroAPI.d.ts for the full DSL.